<section class="suds-process">
  <div class="suds-process__wrap">
    <p class="suds-process__eyebrow">How mobile detailing works</p>
    <h2>Simple scheduling. Clear service levels. Mobile service at your location.</h2>
    <div class="suds-process__grid">
      <article><span>01</span><h3>Choose your detail</h3><p>Book Basic for upkeep, Signature for most first appointments, or Elite Reset for heavier condition.</p></article>
      <article><span>02</span><h3>Request help if needed</h3><p>If the condition is unusual, Suds can recommend the right package before the appointment.</p></article>
      <article><span>03</span><h3>Suds comes to you</h3><p>Your vehicle is detailed at your home, office, or approved location without a shop drop-off.</p></article>
      <article><span>04</span><h3>Protect the result</h3><p>After the reset, ask about maintenance detailing, wax, ceramic protection, or finish upgrades.</p></article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .suds-process { background: #0b0b0b; color: #fff; }
  .suds-process__wrap { max-width: 1180px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 58px 20px; }
  .suds-process__eyebrow { margin: 0 0 10px; color: #f2d36b; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .suds-process h2 { max-width: 860px; margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 4vw, 4.8rem); line-height: 1; letter-spacing: 0; }
  .suds-process__grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0,1fr)); gap: 14px; margin-top: 30px; }
  .suds-process article { padding: 22px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14); border-radius: 8px; background: #141414; }
  .suds-process span { color: #f2d36b; font-weight: 900; }
  .suds-process h3 { margin: 14px 0 10px; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 0; }
  .suds-process p { margin: 0; color: #ededed; font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.5; }
  @media screen and (max-width: 900px) { .suds-process__grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0,1fr)); } }
  @media screen and (max-width: 640px) { .suds-process__wrap { padding: 44px 18px; } .suds-process__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>

{% schema %}
{ "name": "Section process", "settings": [], "presets": [{ "name": "Section process" }] }
{% endschema %}
